dct_title_s: A map of the United States of America agreeable to the peace of 1783
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. "Engraved for Guthries new system of geography." Shows provincial boundaries, Indian villages and tribal territory, rivers and lakes, a few forts and place-names.
